Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.12,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{this is more a "habit" than anything else—}nhưng đó gọi là "thói quen" thì đúng hơn--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:06.97,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:07.82,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{a habit of living creatures.}thói quen của sinh vật sống.
