Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.16,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{you're partly composed of bird thoughts.}cậu có một phần suy nghĩ của loài chim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:15.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:16.76,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Now then,}Giờ thì,
