Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.38,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{what does any of this have to do\N with torturous training?}nó liên quan gì đến việc huấn luyện cực khổ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:17.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.48,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Hayato was actually right.}Hayato nói đúng.
