Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.32,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{His body is already become\Nsomething distinctly inhuman.}Cơ thể cậu ấy đã trở thành thứ gì đó không phải là người.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:21.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.89,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{In exchange, he's gained something\Nthat living creatures do not have:}Đổi lại, cậu ấy có được thứ sinh vật sống không có:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:22.98,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:23.99,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:25.86,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{a metamorphosis which makes \Nhim more effective in combat.}Một sự biến đổi giúp cậu ấy chiến đấu hiệu quả hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:24.99,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
