Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.80,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{The kind of evolution we undergo\N is tied to our own thoughts.}Sự tiến hóa mà chúng ta trải qua\N gắn liền với suy nghĩ của bản thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:26.99,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:27.99,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:30.09,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Wanting to be stronger, \Nhave more resilience, et cetera...}Muốn mạnh mẽ hơn, tăng khả năng phục hồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:28.99,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:29.99,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:32.09,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{And the most efficient way to \Nforce these changes is to expose}Và cách tốt nhất để thay đổi nó
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:30.99,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
