Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:32.99,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{the body to extreme stimuli.}là cơ thể sẽ trở nên kích thích cực hạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:32.99,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\pos(117.143,58.571)\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:36.00,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{So how long does that all take?}Vậy mất bao lâu cho việc đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:39.25,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Somewhere between fifty to a hundred years.}Chắc tầm 50-100 năm gì đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.25,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Sorry. Not happening.}Xin lỗi, không thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:48.61,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, why would you suddenly \Nstart such nuts and bolts training?}Cơ mà sao cậu tự nhiên đòi huấn luyện vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:52.76,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Did seeing a demon in person suddenly\Nmake you realize your responsibility?}Hay thấy ác quỷ khiến cậu\N nghiêm túc nghĩ về trách nhiệm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.77,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Is that what it looks like, Paula?}Trông tớ thế hả, Paula?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:06.03,Italics,Paula,0,0,0,,{That's the face he makes when he's \Ngot something really nasty in mind...}Cái mặt mang đầy suy nghĩ mờ ám...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:10.53,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Hey, Granny, what's that?}Nè bà già, gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.41,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{What's what?}Là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.43,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{You've got something on your clothes.}Bà có cái gì dính sau quần kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:15.72,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Some tiny metal thing.}Một thiết bị nhỏ xíu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:18.16,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{What is this?}Gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.38,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Some kinda machine, maybe?}Một loại máy móc?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.39,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{What's it doing on you, though?}Sao lại dính lên quần bà thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.42,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{I have no idea.}Ai biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:29.34,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{C'mon, what'd you have to break it for? \NYsley might've been able to figure it out.}Sao lại phá nó? Ysley có thể sẽ tìm ra gì đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:33.39,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Doesn't matter. Once it's broken, \Nit's not anything anymore, is it?}Không quan tâm. Phá rồi là xong chuyện, phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:35.83,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Yeah, guess not.}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:38.27,Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,{Oh, but it was.}Làm gì có.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.99,Main,Headline sign,0,0,0,,{\an2\fnArial\fs12\shad0\frz13\fax.1\c&H2C373E&\3c&HF9F6FB&\b1\pos(315.143,156.286)}{Gend Autonomous Zone Invaded and Occupied by Zoble Forces}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:52.36,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Paula, remember how I told you we're born \Nfrom the thoughts of living creatures?}Paula, còn nhớ tớ nói chúng ta sinh ra\N từ suy nghĩ của sinh vật sống không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:56.92,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{The thing is, thoughts alone \Ndon't make us manifest.}Vấn đề là chỉ suy nghĩ thôi sẽ\N không khiến chúng ta sinh ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:59.00,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{It takes an additional element...}Cần thêm một điều kiện...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:01.13,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{A desire for salvation.}Mong muốn được cứu rỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.98,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,{It's okay. Don't be scared.}Không sao, đừng sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.54,Main,Grandma,0,0,0,,{Dear God...}Thần linh ơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.19,Main,Father,0,0,0,,{Please, God...}Làm ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:25.39,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Please... grant us salvation...}Xin hãy cứu rỗi chúng con...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:26.48,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{God!}Thần linh ơi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.49,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{That doesn't make any sense, though.}Vậy thì quá kì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:36.69,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{You said human desire for salvation \Nis what makes Idaten appear,}Cậu nói con người mong muốn\N cứu rỗi nên Idaten xuất hiện,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:39.96,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{but we don't help humans at all.}nhưng chúng ta có cứu giúp ai đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:45.09,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{That's not so strange. It's other humans \Nwho make humans suffer in war, right?}Có gì lạ đâu. Chính con người tự làm tổn\N thương nhau qua chiến tranh, phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:49.21,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{What sense would it make \Nto fight humans to save humans?}Vậy tại sao chúng ta lại chiến đấu\N với con người để cứu con người chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.59,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{I guess you're right...}Phải nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:55.25,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Two human nations fight, \Nand one is destroyed...}Hai quốc gia chiến tranh và một bị phá hủy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:59.22,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{The victor grows in its place, \Nso it's not a problem.}Kẻ thắng sẽ tiếp tục bành trướng, chẳng có gì sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:02.80,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{It's not as if the humans care about how \Nthe composition of a forest might change}Ngay cả con người cũng chả\N quan tâm khu rừng thay đổi thế nào
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:04.73,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{as long as there are still plants there.}miễn là vẫn còn cây ở đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:08.03,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{And if an invasive species wipes \Nout the native wildlife of a lake,}Và nếu một loài xâm lấn xóa sổ\N sinh vật bản địa trong một cái hồ,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.24,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{they'd just think of it \Nas a good fishing spot.}họ cũng chỉ nghĩ "ồ, chỗ này nhiều cá nè" thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:13.06,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{This is all to say that, \Nwhile we're in a different position,}Tóm lại là tuy chúng ta đứng ở vị trí khác nhau,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:16.50,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{our thought process isn't \Nso different from the humans'.}nhưng cách suy nghĩ không khác \Nso với con người là mấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:21.50,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Still, there's a condition under which\Nwe will fight to protect them.}Tuy nhiên, vẫn có một trường hợp\N chúng ta sẽ chiến đấu bảo vệ họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.40,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Consider the demons...}Liên quan đến ác quỷ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:29.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{For example, say you happened upon that Gyudo\Nmonster attacking some humans.}Ví dụ như nếu Gyudo tấn công con người,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:32.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{If you were as powerful as Rin-san,\N what would you do?}nếu cậu có sức mạnh như Rin-san thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.01,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{I think I'd get rid of him.}Tớ sẽ xử lý nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:38.84,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Yet why would you help humans \Nthat you normally just ignore?}Sao cậu lại giúp con người thay vì bỏ qua?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.99,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Huh, that's a good question...\N I wonder.}Ủa? Sao vậy nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:45.38,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{I guess because I'd feel\N compelled to fight the monster?}Vì tớ cảm thấy phải chiến đấu với nó?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:48.84,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Wrong. It's because if you do nothing,\Nthe humans would be wiped out.}Sai. Vì nếu không làm gì, con người sẽ bị tiêu diệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:53.02,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Humans are similar. If a forest they \Nnormally don't care about catches on fire,}Con người cũng thế. Nếu khu rừng\N họ không quan tâm bị cháy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.03,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{they'll make an effort to put it out.}họ sẽ nỗ lực chữa cháy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:58.66,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{But right now, mankind is distinctly \N}{\i1}{not}{\i0}{ on the brink of destruction.}Ngay bây giờ, nhân loại không trên bờ vực diệt vong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.49,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{They're prosperous enough}Họ đủ sung túc
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.95,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{to kill one another for simple \Nself-interest, of all things.}để giết nhau chỉ vì mục đích cá nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:08.63,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{And as humans engage in pointless \Nwars to amuse themselves,}Và con người tham gia vào những cuộc\N chiến tranh vô nghĩa như thú vui,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:11.05,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{the collective thoughts of those\N caught in the crossfire}và suy nghĩ của những kẻ bị mắc kẹt trong trận chiến
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:14.55,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{is what calls us forth... to do nothing.}là thứ kêu gọi chúng ta... không làm gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.55,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Thus we do nothing.}Vì thế chúng ta không làm gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:20.72,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{I suppose you could say we're a generation \Nof Idaten deities who only know peace.}Đó là thế hệ của các Idaten chúng ta,\N những người chỉ biết đến hòa bình.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:30.71,Italics,Gill,0,0,0,,{Is there no God after all?}Chẳng có thần linh nào cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:36.32,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Still, there's something I don't understand.\N What purpose do the demons serve?}Nhưng tớ vẫn không hiểu ác quỷ tồn tại để làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:37.83,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{Did you know, Paula?}Cậu có biết không, Paula?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:42.33,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{If left uncontested, \Nthey'd continue to predate and destroy}Nếu không ngăn chặn thì chúng sẽ tiếp tục phá hủy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:45.85,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{until the world was completely barren}cho đến khi thế giới trở nên cằn cỗi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.33,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{and they ultimately died from starvation.}và cuối cùng chúng chết vì đói.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.95,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{It doesn't make any sense.}Thật vô nghĩa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:55.34,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{If there are any intelligent \Ndemons out there...}Nếu có ác quỷ có trí thông minh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.89,Main,Ys,0,0,0,,{I would love to ask what they want.}tớ muốn hỏi mục đích của chúng là gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:04.77,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{Hey! Pi-chan, Pi-chan!}Nè Pi-chan! Pi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:08.27,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{Long time no see! \NYou been doin' good, yeah?}Đã lâu không gặp! Vẫn khỏe chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:11.15,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{It's been a few years since \NI last saw you, right? Right?!}Đã vài năm từ lần cuối rồi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:14.00,Italics,Piscala,0,0,0,,{The way she talks is still annoying.}Vẫn ồn ào như mọi khi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.11,Main,Piscala,0,0,0,,Nickel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:18.15,Main,Piscala,0,0,0,,{You need to show more respect \Nto a superior officer!}Cô phải thể hiện sự nghiêm túc với một sĩ quan cấp cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.66,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, you're right!}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:27.79,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{I need'st be formal with my manner \Nof speech, do I not, General Piscalat?!}Phải cư xử đúng đắn nhỉ, chỉ huy Piscalat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:31.79,Main,Troop,0,0,0,,{How'd she survive a fall from that height?}Nhảy từ trên đó xuống sao vẫn còn sống vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:36.29,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{Putting that aside, this meeting \Nshould be of incredible import!}Bỏ qua đi, nghe nói lần họp này quan trọng lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:40.30,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{I dare say we're in for the first \Nmeeting of substance in quite some time!}Đã lâu không tham gia một cuộc họp rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:45.23,Main,Biarov,0,0,0,,{Your Majesty,}Thưa bệ hạ,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:48.73,Caption base,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs16\pos(160.571,61.143)\fad(1270,1)}{Prime Minister of the Zoble Empire\N}{\fs30}{Biarov}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:48.73,Main,Biarov,0,0,0,,{why am I not a part of this meeting?}tại sao tôi không được tham gia cuộc họp?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.37,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Because it has nothing to do with you.}Vì ngươi không liên quan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:55.46,Caption base,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs12\pos(556,198.286)\fad(1005,1000)}{Emperor of the Zoble Empire\N}{\fs24}{Takeshita}Hoàng đế Zoble\N Takeshita
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:55.46,Caption base,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs12\fad(1005,1000)\pos(57.143,234.286)}{Empress\N}{\fs24}{Brandy}Nữ hoàng \N Brandy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:54.29,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{That's right. Your job is running \Nthe government, isn't it?}Phải đó, việc của ngươi là bên chính trị.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:57.24,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Just focus on policy and diplomacy.}Tập trung vào ngoại giao đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:00.81,Italics,Biarov,0,0,0,,{What the hell kind of diplomacy could a \Nwar-mongering nation like this manage?}Cái quốc gia gây chiến liên tục thì ngoại giao cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:03.37,Main,Biarov,0,0,0,,{As you wish, ma'am.}Vâng thưa ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:07.38,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{Hey there, Your Majesty the Emperor!}Chào bệ hạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:11.78,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{You're looking as miserable as ever!}Ngài vẫn khắc khổ như mọi khi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:15.10,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{We'll be waiting in the\N meeting room! Bye-bye!}Chúng tôi vào trước nhé! Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:19.71,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{I must say, formal language is most tiring,\N don't you think, General Piscalat?!}Cơ mà cái ngôn ngữ này nói mệt nhỉ, chỉ huy Piscalat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:21.34,Main,Piscala,0,0,0,,{You're not even pulling it off.}Cô không yên một chút được à.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:24.54,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Nickel certainly seems to be in high spirits.}Nickel có vẻ hào hứng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.07,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{We should get going ourselves.}Chúng ta cũng đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.70,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Yes, I suppose we should.}Ờ. Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:33.85,Italics,Biarov,0,0,0,,{This meeting was called by Obami,\N head of weapons development...}Cuộc gặp này được tổ chức bởi Obami, \Nngười đứng đầu bộ phát triển vũ khí...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:36.93,Italics,Biarov,0,0,0,,{What is that madman's game now?}Lão ta đang suy tính điều gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:37.94,Main,Biarov,0,0,0,,Kagekiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:38.57,Main,Kage,0,0,0,,Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:41.19,Main,Biarov,0,0,0,,{I want you to look into this.}Ngươi hãy điều tra cho ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:43.07,Main,Kage,0,0,0,,{By your command.}Tuân lệnh ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.07,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\b1\shad0\bord0\pos(323.429,112.857)\c&H08090C&}{Meeting Room}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:47.29,Caption base,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs12\fad(1005,1)\pos(273.143,314.857)}{Commander of the Zoble Imperial Navy\N}{\fs18}{Neput}Chỉ huy Hải quân\N Neput
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:47.29,Caption base,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs12\fad(1005,1)\pos(100.571,157.143)}{Child Soldier\N}{\fs18}{Cory}Quân nhân trẻ\N Cory
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:50.00,Caption base,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs12\fad(1005,1)\pos(409.143,46.857)}{Zoble Army Defense Force Soldier\N}{\fs18}{G-Thirteen}Lực lượng phòng vệ\N G-13
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:50.00,Caption base,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs12\fad(1005,1)\pos(553.715,199.429)}{The Lively Chief Clerk\Nof Childcare Support\N}{\fs18}{Barcode}Thư kí trưởng\N Barcode
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:50.00,Caption base,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs12\fad(1005,1)\pos(142.286,230.857)}{Star Midwife\N}{\fs18}{Umeyo}Phòng sản xuất\N Umeyo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.25,Caption base,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(111.429,77.714)\fs16\fad(1005,1)}{Animal Trainer\N}{\fs24}{Miku}Người luyện thú\N Miku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.50,Caption base,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(323.429,212.571)}{And everybody else}Và những người khác
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.55,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{Is that everyone?}Tất cả đây à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:57.50,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{The doctor's not here yet.}Vẫn còn tiến sĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:20:01.63,Caption base,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs12\fad(1005,1)\pos(81.714,76.571)}{PM Biarov's Personal Agent\N}{\fs18}{Kagekiki the Ninja}Nhẫn giả \Ncục tình báo\N Kagekiki
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:01.63,Italics,Kage,0,0,0,,{What a bizarre assemblage...}Một tập hợp kì lạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.95,Italics,Kage,0,0,0,,{What do they mean to discuss?}Chúng muốn làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:08.93,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Sorry about the delay, folks.}Xin lỗi vì đến trễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.94,Caption base,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1005,1)\fs16\pos(465.143,198.857)}{Head of Weapons Development\N}{\fs24}{Doctor Obami}Cục trưởng cục phát triển vũ khí\N Tiến sĩ Obami
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:11.94,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Let's get this meeting underway.}Bắt đầu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.25,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{What happened to you...?}Ông bị gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:24.16,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Shut it! My usual body got \Nwrecked by that Idaten brat!}Im đi! Cơ thể ta bị thằng nhãi Idaten phá rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:27.06,Italics,Kage,0,0,0,,{His "usual body"? It was wrecked?}Cơ thể? Bị phá?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:29.54,Italics,Kage,0,0,0,,{And what exactly is an Idaten?}Idaten là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:33.84,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Granted, that's part of why \Nwe're having this meeting.}Mà thôi, đó cũng là lý do cuộc họp này.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:35.81,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{First, let's start with...}Đầu tiên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:38.11,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{Oh, can I take care of one thing first?}Khoan đã, trước đó thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.42,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{What is it, Nickel?}Chuyện gì Nickel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:50.72,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{Would you look at that!\NIf isn't Kagekiki-kun!}Ai thế này? Kagekiki đây mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:53.73,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{Look, I understand being curious...}Tôi hiểu là cậu tò mò...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.73,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{But eavesdropping is just rude!}Nhưng nghe lén là xấu lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.78,Main,Nickel,0,0,0,,{Oh, sorry about that, Take-kun.}Xin lỗi nhé Take.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.70,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Try to be more careful.}Cẩn thận hơn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.53,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Now, we're ready when you are...}Giờ thì bắt đầu thôi nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:13.54,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{O great Demon Lord who granted \Nus human forms and intelligence.}Chúa quỷ vĩ đại, người đã ban cho\N chúng ta trí thông minh và dạng người.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:17.48,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{All right, let's start by reviewing \Nthe footage of the Idaten.}Rồi, vậy thì hãy xem qua đoạn video của Idaten.
